pdftron.PDF

Class Image2RGB

  • java.lang.Object
    • pdftron.Filters.Filter
      • pdftron.PDF.Image2RGB

  • public class Image2RGB
extends Filter
    Image2RGB is a filter that can decompress and normalize any PDF image stream (e.g. monochrome, CMYK, etc) into a raw RGB pixel stream.
